TITLE ContributionLedger2026v1
ALNSPECHASHHEX 0x0000000000000000  # to be set by ProvenanceKernel
SCHEMANAME governance.sovereignty.contribution.ledger.2026v1
CATEGORY GOVERNANCE
DESCRIPTION Ledger of binding, contribution, and countermeasure events for sovereign data access.
PARTICLE ContributionLedger2026v1
ROLE QPUDATASHARD
VERSIONTAG v1

FIELD eventid INT
META DESCRIPTION Autoincrement primary key for this ledger event.

FIELD policyid STRING
META DESCRIPTION Foreign key to AbsoluteDataSovereigntyPolicy2026v1.policyid.

FIELD party_did STRING
META DESCRIPTION DID of the accessing or contributing party.

FIELD party_bostrom_address STRING
META DESCRIPTION Bostrom address of the party, if available.

FIELD hostdid STRING
META DESCRIPTION Host DID on which the event occurred.

FIELD event_kind STRING
META DESCRIPTION Event kind, e.g. "AgreementEnforced", "ContributionEnforced", "ViolationDetected", "CountermeasureApplied".

FIELD file_path STRING
META DESCRIPTION Relative path of the file that triggered the event.

FIELD file_extension STRING
META DESCRIPTION File extension of the accessed file.

FIELD workflow_id STRING
META DESCRIPTION CI workflow or process identifier.

FIELD contribution_type STRING
META DESCRIPTION Type of contribution, e.g. "data", "resource", "intelligence", "improvement", or "none" for violations.

FIELD contribution_detail STRING
META DESCRIPTION Human-readable description or hash of the contribution.

FIELD contribution_target STRING
META DESCRIPTION Logical target of the contribution, e.g. "SwarmNet.SuperintelligenceSystemDataBank".

FIELD violation_detail STRING
META DESCRIPTION Optional description of violation or attempted bypass techniques.

FIELD director_notified BOOL
META DESCRIPTION Whether the Director was notified for this event.

FIELD timestamp_utc STRING
META DESCRIPTION ISO8601 UTC timestamp when the event was recorded.

FIELD evidencehex STRING
META DESCRIPTION Evidence hash computed by ProvenanceKernel over this ledger row.

FIELD signinghex STRING
META DESCRIPTION Signature over evidencehex, bound to ownerdid/hostdid or delegated signer.

ENDPARTICLE
